high_descs: Walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the leftmost bottle of lotion off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk towards the shower, then hang a left and walk forward, turn left to face the toilet.
Put the bottle of lotion in the small green bin to the left of the toilet.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the toilet tank.
Walk over to the small green bin that is to the left of the toilet.
Put the bottle of lotion into the small green bin.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion into a green bin.

high_descs: Go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the green bin.
Take the pump bottle on the left from the toilet tank.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn left, go forward a step, turn left to face the toilet.
Put the pump bottle in the green bin to the left of the toilet.
Turn right, go forward a step, turn left, go towards the space between the toilet and sink.
Take the pump bottle from the toilet tank.
Go back to the front of the toilet, face the toilet.
Put the pump bottle in the green bin to the left of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put two pump bottles in a green bin.

high_descs: Go forward to the wall, then turn right to go to the toilet.
Pick up the leftmost bottle of soap from the back of the toilet.
Go to the trash bin to your left.
Put the bottle of soap in the trash bin.
Go to the toilet to your right.
Pick up the bottle of soap from the back of the toilet.
Go to the trash bin to your left.
Put the bottle of soap in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of soap in the trash.
